    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Cursed:  If he owns anything more complex than a knife, item rapidly deteriorates and becomes inoperable within an hour.  
Must inform Garou if Kindred are going into their territory without permission and kill them if possible.  Phone number pops into his head and he forgets after dials.
Forgets all Garou lore.  If hears new lore forgets it immediately after.  Knows there are people who are kind of like werewolves known as Garou.
Linguistics- Itiallian, German, Spanish, Latin
Anarch Rep- Soldier, Committed *2, Unreliable, Casualty.
Owed 1 hour in the Giovanni Library.
Owed 2 ward vs Wraith from Shiva.
Bestial Traits- Feathers and Owl Eyes
Get out of status trouble from Harpy.
Status help from Prince.
1st level of dementation
2 boxes of Gia's Marbels]]>
    </notes>
