      <![CDATA[Cock-Robin's Motivations-  Searching for Red List person, Slaughter of Nosferatu 11 years ago, hatred of the Sabbat, Should the Camarilla fight to hold Phoenix?

Looking for member of the Red List.  Thinks Phoenix should be used as a stepping stone to attack Sabbat in Mexico.  Member of Gehenna Cult- looking for new members.  Former member of the Josians.  Not too fond of Anarchs, think they lack both spine and vision.]]>
