    <notes>
      <![CDATA[You obey an order from Ashevelaker without hesitation or question.  Your brothers and sisters are your family and your life; you move and act as one to protect each other and your Sire.  If you are insulted or threatened, your first reaction is violence.

You have the Rending.  It is bad.  It hurts a whole lot.  Have fun.]]>
