    <notes>
      <![CDATA[2.3 Equipment:
Sports Car-  Only fits two people
Armor Plated
Bullet proof windows

Twin machine guns (front)
  +4 traits
   - loud
   6 lethal

Smoke Screen
  When activated, a thick smoke screen billows out from behind the car.,   Treat as Shroud of Darkness.

Ejection Seat-  Ejects Driver and Passanger seats 100' into the air.  Parachute to land safely.

Self-Destruct
  After given the password car will blow up in 10 seconds.
]]>
    </notes>
  </vampire>
