    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Your character is at this gathering because(many of these are covert):
a Higher up sent you here to manipulate the Camarilla into giving up Phoenix
Rumors of Lilith Cult in Phoenix
Local Assets:
Trivial boon of the Tremere
Minor boon of the Nosferatu Clan in Phoenix
Old list of contacts in Phoenix
Gun hidden in your luggage
Knows of or knows:ELIJAH  , RAYMUND  , JAMEY  , THANE  , VALDA  , BECCI  , EDWYN  , EVERETTE  , LINZI  , SHELLEY  , KORINA  , 
Here are a few words that others have used that might describe this character: multi-valued, miwok,at large, blossom forth,warmed-over, gruidae,reprehensively, tag on,megalomanic, formosa,from scratch, jut out]]>
    </notes>
