      <![CDATA[Your character is at this gathering because(many of these are covert):
a Higher up sent you here to manipulate the Camarilla into giving up Phoenix
Personal enemy also has an invitation
Local Assets:
Phone number for the Phoenix Anarch Leader
Map of the Sewers(not warrens)
Book of Camarilla Lore (Cam Lore 3) 
List of 10 Sabbat Operatives in the United States
Knows of or knows:FAITH  , JAMEY  , THANE  , GRAEME  , NORBERT  , KENNETH  , CIEL  , FULK  , SEBASTIAN  , LINTON  , AMALIA  , KORINA  , 
Here are a few words that others have used that might describe this character: incidental to, preventative,not only, take control,countrywide, pellitory-of-the-wall,showing wisdom, sensify,dispiriting, claxon,at once, doze off]]>
