    <other>
      <![CDATA[Investments:  
Cause Vertigo:  Requires a Mental Challenge; target must make a Static Physical Challenge (vs. 5 Traits just to stand, 7 to take any actions) or collapse, balance shot.

Hell-Skinned:  Immune to all natural flames and heat (including dragonsbreath rounds and flamethrowers).  Does not protect against magical flame.

Kiss of Hades:  Spend 1 Blood; cause two aggravated wounds with a kiss.

Psychic Tracker:  May track a given target through clairaudience (hears them over distance).  1 Blood per hour used.

Razor Fingers:  Spend 1 Blood; may cause 2 aggravated wounds in hand-to-hand combat.

Smell Fear:  Spend 1 Blood; may sense fear in a target within 100 feet.

Teleportation:  Spend 1 Blood; may teleport anywhere within 100 feet.

Walk the Walls:  May walk or crawl on any surface capable of supporting her weight.]]>
    </other>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Disciplines: 
 Auspex:  Heightened Senses, Aura Perception, Spirit's Touch, Telepathy, Psychic Projection, Soul Scan
Celerity:  Alacrity, Swiftness, Rapidity, Fleetness, Quickness
Dominate:  Command, Forgetful Mind, Mesmerism, Conditioning, Possession, Obedience
Fortitude:  Endurance, Mettle, Resilience, Aegis, Imperviousness
Obtenebration:  Shadow Play, Shroud of Night, Arms of the Abyss, Shadow Body
Potence:  Prowess, Might, Vigor, Puissance, Virility
Presence:  Dread Gaze, Entrancement, Summon, Majesty, Love]]>
    </notes>
  </various>
