    <notes>
      <![CDATA[ST NOTE:
******************************************
Want e-mail explination of how    character is working to get    background of CONTACTS.***

Malkavian Combo Discipline : Prophecy : Cost 10xp ( Aspex lvl 4 + Dementation lvl 3 )

Requires Static test vs Character Mentals. Plus the spending of one blood trait.

Doing any Prophecy takes one full hour. If interupted will automaticlly be unnsuccessfull.

Simple information = 5 traits

Not Simple, but Not Complex Information = 8 traits

Complex Information = 11 traits

Highly Detailed Information = 14 traits

ST/ Narrator will determine information Difficulity.

Retest with Awareness or Investigation.

Loss = You get lost in the madness - primary derrangement activates.

Tie = Somewhat successful - person you are doing Prophecy for gets one free Prophecy retest for the evening.

Win = Your are able to give your person a good Prophecy of the furture - person receiving this Prophecy will get three free Prophecy retests during the evening.]]>
    </notes>
  </vampire>
