    <other>
      <![CDATA[Spell to get a person lost.  Social challenge vs target if target looses they become lost and can't find where they are going.  Other people can physically take target places but target gets lost always when by self.  Even when going to another room.

If Grinch witnesses an act of Selflessness by someone he is effected as if by Dread Gaze.

When in the presence of a Grinch a character temporaraly looses 1 Humanity (max of one humanity a night and can't drop below 1)

When in the presence of a Grinch it takes 4 static challenges to stake a Vampire.

Any characters with a submissive trait grow an antler when in the presence of a Grinch.]]>
    </other>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Grinches are created when Santa or one of his helpers causes Paradox.  One is created for every level.  These spirits will avoid Santa and helpers and instead target those the santa's are helping.
They start with doing small annoyances and gradually increase to seriousness.]]>
    </notes>
  </various>
