    <notes>
      <![CDATA[2.3 Equipment:
Treasure:  Shadow Veil
This delicate and simple-seeming piece of veiling allows its wearer to become invisible as per the rules for Basic Obtenebration: Shadow Play.
Bunks
1. Dust to Dust:  Blow a pinch of dust at the target. [1]
2. Ashes to Ashes:  Mark the target with a smudge of ash. [2]
3.  Broken Dream:  Shatter a piece of glass no smaller than your palm. [3]
4.  Wind Knots:  Tie 3 knots in a piece of silk string; untie them all in reverse order. [4]
5.  Twist of Fate:  Braid 3 strands of spiderweb; drape the braid on the target. [5]]]>
    </notes>
  </changeling>
