    <biography>
      <![CDATA[Wife and family murdered before his eyes, was Forgetful Minded to forget the faces.  Wants to find those responsible.  He has spent many a night speaking with Father Andrew within the church at St. Louis, and simply wants to avenge the memory of his beloved family.]]>
    </biography>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Since the death of Father Andrew, he has become more unstable.  He continues to plan the death of the Giovanni, and is working hand in hand with the Sons of Tertillian.]]>
    </notes>
  </mortal>
