    <boon type="Life Boon" partner="Lamar Duvalier" owed="yes" date="4/12/2008"/>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[(Jing Xuan Shi)
Tiger Tatoo-  Jet is 1 trait up on any challenge to find 'the Truth'
Oath-  Protect all Children

Hasten:  Elder level Celerity.  Character gets free Hasten retest on any test involving speed.  Hasten is always the last retest for character. 1 blood activates this power and all lower Celerity powers.
Languages- Japanese(native), English, Ancient Chinese (Court Mandarin), Arabic, Mandarin Chinese, Russian, Latin, French, Italian, Filipino (tagalog), spanish, german, latin, ASL, and High Elvish.
Owns:
Midland Credit Managment (collection agency)
Moonlighter's Collections (repo)
Right Now Investigations

Curse-  Pass on a secret the betrayal will follow

Learning up to Pussance from Paris

Viscisitude by Paulo
+2 Steps
+3 Health levels
Retractable Knuckle spurs ward vs kindred

Soul Painting: Must be done on Bob the computer. Must have had at least one hour of one on one time with the subject. Besides given effects from the Toreador clanbook, 2nd ed., grants the effect of a know the subjects current emotional state and grants a view of the person from 5 feet above.  this requires 30 minutes of study of the finished work. can screen capture up to 1 minute of the scry.

Path of Bushido
Conviction/Self-Control/Courage
1- Breaking your word to Liege Lord.  Breaking Sacred Oath.
2- Treating a Superior with disrespect.  Failure to Follow Liege Lord's Orders.
3- Failing to provide Hospitality to allies and clan mates.  Failure to answer an insult.
4- Failing to assist peers or clan mates in need.  Breaking your word to clan mate or peer.
5- Placing personal desire above duty.  Treating a peer with disrespect.]]>
    </notes>
  </vampire>
