    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Real Name: Robert Cooper
Camarilla Name: Mathew Webster
Sabbat Name: Bob
All Identities are Malkavian.
Was embraced Sabbat and converted to the Camarilla when the change over occured due to being abandoned by the Sabbatndf
4th In-Clan/Inceptor Discipline is Mytherceria 2nd Ed.  Languages: Nahuatl/Aztec, Italian, Ancient Babylonian, Latin, Greek, German, Gaelic, Arabic.  Robert's Sabbat pack speak Aztec.  The phoenix malkavians speak Greek.  15th Gens: Can't Blood Bond People, Embrace, Make Ghouls.  They also Take Lethal not Agg from Sun Light.  I can't be blood bound by anyone (read Unbondable).  (Schlacta Mods: 5 extra health Lv. across entire body. 4 extra health levels on torso, total 9 extra HL on Torso.  3lv. Organic Weapons: Claws, and forarm spikes. 3 lv speed enhancement total +6 steps per action.
April 21 2006 Get Powers from Demon, start Develeping Path of Blood per MET ST guide.  Tremere Thaum, Via Path of Unknown.
May 14th 2006 is when Cam Reset happens.
Begin Golconda trainning with Simon Trent July 8, 2006.
September 9th, 2006: Received tatoo from Shiva that randomly makes him loose this advantages from being a thin-blood.
March 10th, 2007 Shiva removes old tattoo and does three Advanced level Tattoos working together to make an even more powerful ritual.  Benifits of Super Tattoo:  All disciplines are treated as in-clan for xp cost.  All disciplines may be learned without a teacher provided I have clan lore of 3 or more in that clan.  I can learn any clan combo power as long as I have the Clan Lore at 3 and disciplines needed.  Blood magic: I can learn first path to first int.  But all other paths are basic.  Thaum and Necro are seperate for this purpose.
April 15th, 2007.  Start inventing ritual that encrypts existing documents, or encrypts documents as they are being written; can be combined with scribe ritual, or used as a scribe ritual.]]>
    </notes>
  </vampire>
