    <biography>
      <![CDATA[During the late 1800's was the goule of Vladamer Putin.  During the peoples uprising Mikhael in a move to grab power killed Vladamer used his blood to turn himself.  During WWII was recrited into the KGB.  When the belin wall fell and the Soviet union fell apart mickhael became part of the rushan mafia.]]>
    </biography>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Nicknamed "the Russian"
Languages- Russian(native), German, English
Mentor-  Brujah non-elder
Part Owner of a Winery in Paradise Valley.  4pt communal Ventrue haven.
Learning up to Intensity from Azure McFee.
Learning pussance from Paris.
Owes minor favor to Lorenzo Giovanni.

Purchased 51% Of New Times

Access to Asimite Lore

Owes Jessy a minor boon]]>
    </notes>
  </vampire>
