    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Tribal Adv for Uktena: Umbral Sight.
Personal Totem: Bear, Brawny Permanetly, medicine x 3, mothers touch once per day.  Hibernate for 3 months at a time.  Lose 5 honor and all honor in the future is 1 less in awards.
Pack Totem: Chimara, enigmas x 3, mental trait insightful permanently, can disguse in umbra, 2 wisdom, 2 bonus in enigma.
Caern Totem: Owl: wings in umbra, 2 trait bonus for stealth like abitlies, 3 trait bonus for gifts of stealth like things.
Tribal Totem: Uktena: 1 level of armor in the umbra, two wisdom, 1 xp per story for mystical stuff.
Fetishes are in the form of Scar Fetishes and they are: Spirit of the Birds, Grandmother's touch, Scrying, Hand of Earth Lords, Reshape object.
Languages: Lucumi, Pictish, Glyphs,]]>
    </notes>
  </werewolf>
