    <other>
      <![CDATA[Immune to Dementation, Dominate and Presence, as well as Serpentis: Eyes of the Serpent, and Auspex: Telepathy.]]>
    </other>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Built per Clanbook Giovanni, Revised edition, page 56. for  Zombies animated through use of Necromancy: Path of Bone: Shambling Hordes.
"Most shamblers are unaffected by mental Disciplines - or, indeed, any mental coercion - at all." ... "Immune to Dementation, Dominate and Presence, as well as Serpentis: Eyes of the Serpent, and Auspex: Telepathy. Shamblers have a normal health level track but do not suffer any penalties due to wounds." ...Clanbook Giovanni p.56

Guards the Giovanni Haven.  In the Basement.  Paris sleeps with them around him.]]>
    </notes>
  </various>
