    <traitlist name="Health Levels" abc="no" display="1">
      <trait name="Healthy" val="3"/>
      <trait name="Bruised" val="3"/>
      <trait name="Wounded" val="2"/>
      <trait name="Incapacitated"/>
      <trait name="Destroyed"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Powers" abc="no" atomic="yes" display="5">
      <trait name="Fortitude" note="Endurance"/>
      <trait name="Fortitude" note="Mettle"/>
      <trait name="Fortitude" note="Resilience"/>
      <trait name="Damage" note="3 lethal"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Equipment" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Locations" abc="yes" atomic="yes" display="5">
      <trait name="Giovanni Castle"/>
    </traitlist>
    <other>
      <![CDATA[Immune to Dementation, Dominate and Presence, as well as Serpentis: Eyes of the Serpent, and Auspex: Telepathy.]]>
    </other>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Built per Clanbook Giovanni, Revised edition, page 56. for  Zombies animated through use of Necromancy: Path of Bone: Shambling Hordes.
"Most shamblers are unaffected by mental Disciplines - or, indeed, any mental coercion - at all." ... "Immune to Dementation, Dominate and Presence, as well as Serpentis: Eyes of the Serpent, and Auspex: Telepathy. Shamblers have a normal health level track but do not suffer any penalties due to wounds." ...Clanbook Giovanni p.56
Szlachta Modifications: 3 total modification levels, per. LOTN Sabbat Guide, pp. 177-179.
- 2 levels of "Organic Weapons" = Serrated Bone Spikes, inflicts a total of 3 levels of lethal damage per strike.
- 1 level of "Enhanced Speed" = Zombies may take two extra steps during combat movement..

Guards the Giovanni Haven.  In the Basement.  Paris sleeps with them around him.]]>
    </notes>
  </various>
