      <![CDATA[Medium Gold Chalice.  Large enough to take 2 hands to hold.]]>
    </appearance>
  </item>
  <item name="Claw/Stun Cestus" type="Equipment" subtype="Weapon" level="0" bonus="2" damage="Aggravated" amount="1" conceal="None" lastmodified="3/22/2003 2:01:34 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Clumsy"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Bonus Traits: 2 Neg Trait: Short Range: Touch   Damage:  1 additional level Aggravated  

When striking target with a closed fist, acts as stun knuckles. Bonus Traits: 2 Neg Trait: Short Range: Touch Damage:  1 additional level Lethal Damage The impact ridges of the knuckles are more extended than normal and the inner edge has a metal cylinder that works as a "fist load" and contains a high charge capacitor.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Gloves designed from Kevlar/nomex weave.  Across the tops of the bottom joint of each finger are small metal plates attached to a taser charge.  In the first joint of each finger are small (3/4') blades and tubing which leads to a small acid reservoir in the glove.  The blades are extended by flexing the fingers.  A sucessful strike causes the blades to scratch the skin and a small amount of acid to flow into the wound.  The acid causes aggravated damage and an intense burning sensation.]]>
    </appearance>
  </item>
