  <item name="Exploding Bazooka Boots" type="Equipment" subtype="Weapon" level="0" bonus="1" damage="Lethal" amount="1" conceal="None" lastmodified="3/22/2003 1:59:06 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Clumsy"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Unique"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Boot Tip: Injector Launcher consists of 2 tubes fitted with modified Incendiary Cylinder Grenades  or Injectors with pointed tips. The grenades are notched to allow them to lock into place in the tubes. Spring loaded.  Trigger mechanism : On impact, injects/implants grenade into the target and activates 5 second delay fuse.
Heels: compartment for Disk Grenade.  Loaded through side slot.  Stomping down on heel triggers grenade. (Smoke Grenade) These grenades fill roughly a large room-sized area (10' x 10' x 10') with thick black smoke.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Steel Tipped Boots]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Damage: Right:  Thermite grenades cause one level of aggravated damage to their target. Unless extinguished with a Static Physical Challenge (six-Trait difficulty to simulate rolling around or beat out the flames), the Thermite continue to inflict one level of aggravated damage for 3 turns (approximately 12 seconds).> Left: Target injected with fluid within injector, normally 1 trait of Justin's blood]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
