  </item>
  <item name="Marble Grenades - Rotter" type="Equipment" subtype="Ranged Weapon" level="0" bonus="1" damage="Aggravated" amount="1" conceal="Pocket" lastmodified="3/19/2003 1:44:04 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Spray"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Tiny"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Unique"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[75%/25% Concentrated formula of hydrofluoric acid and acetone. A successful hit causes one level of aggravated damage to the target. As the acid quickly permeates the skin and begins necrosis of the tissue and bone structure, the actetone begins defatting the skin tissue, causing the target to gain the negative Physical Trait: Clumsy or Lame as the tissue, muscle and bone of the affected limb is destroyed. By making two successful Simple Tests (win only) after a successful hit, the target's head is struck. Doing so kill mortals instantly and causes Kindred to gain the negative Mental Traits: Oblivious and Witless in addition to rendering them unable to use the powers of Celerity, Fortitude and Potence.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[1 " diameter gold sphere]]>
    </appearance>
  </item>
