    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Bonus Traits: 2 traits Negative Trait: Clumsy, flammable. 
Range: Range: 15 feet.  Sprays a small burst of flame capable of striking only a single target.  A Successful hit inflicts One (1) level  of Aggravated Damage then the flames snuff out. (Similar to Flame Bolt)
Special Ability:  Incendiary.  Damage caused by this weapon is fire based (aggravated).]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Glove:  insulated/flame retardant tube running from the tip of the first finger of the glove back to attach to the reservoir.  An electrical igniter is built into the tip of the tube to ignite the spray as it leaves the tube.  
Reservoir: 5 inches wide. 3/4" thick.  Consists of 8 cartridges filled with pressurized "napalm" mixture.]]>
    </appearance>
  </item>
