    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Incendiary- Simple test to cause additional level of aggravated damage and target starts on fire.  Must spend 1 ACTION to put fire out.  Kindred must win a self-control test or go into Fire Frenzy. 
Poison- Simple test to cause additional level of aggravated damage to living creatures and additional aggravated every 20 minutes until she receives proper medical treatment.
Created by Shiva.  Owner must figure out how to control snake.
Traits- Quick, Sharp, Lithe, Resilient.
Very territorial  will attack anyone who comes in its territory.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[3 foot long Rattlesnake with full body tattoos.]]>
