    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Talismans" val="3"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[When applied to the tongue, the Gypsy gains the additional Social Traits: Beguiling x2 in regards to all Social Manipulation tests. When applied to the face and eyelids, the Rom gains the additional Social Traits of Alluring x2. If applied to the tips of the fingers, he gains the Physical Traits of Nimble x2.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[This light green tincture grants the Rom the charismatic gifts of the legendary fork-tongued reptile.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[The effects last for one scene.  There are three (3) applications per jar.]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
