    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Incapacitation: On a successful hit, the target is considered Incapacitated.  The character loses their next action (not full turn- characters with Celerity may very well get up within the same turn) and gains the Negative Physical Trait: Clumsy x2 and the negative Mental Trait: Witless x2.  These negative traits are temporary and lost at the rate of one Clumsy and one Witless per subsequent action (not full turn- characters with high enough (Elder level) Celerity may very well recover within the turn).]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Hand held device that delivers a high powered electrical charge into the target.]]>
    </appearance>
  </item>
