    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[The impact ridges of the knuckles are more extended than normal and the inner edge has a metal cylinder that works as a "fist load" and contains a high charge capacitor.  The T-Wave has been modified to effect specifically nervous system activity.   The capacitor is good for 12 hours then must be recharged.]]>
