  <item name="Whuzo Ointment" type="Talisman" subtype="Draba" level="2" bonus="0" amount="0" lastmodified="1/25/2004 5:30:42 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2">
      <trait name="Power" val="3"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Talismans" val="2"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[This balm can remove any impurities tainting a person. Such impurities include non-magical poisons and disease and Kindred blood (that has resulted in Blood Bonding or Ghouling), but do not include such things as changing a vampire back into human form.]]>
    </powers>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Each jar of the ointment contains three (3) doses.   In regards to the Bond, each application only removes one step of the Bond.  The balm can only be applied to any given individual once per night.  The ointment is applied to the site of the infection or over the heart.  As the ointment works, the contaminant seeps into the balm through the skin.]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
